<br>
I don't want five people controlling the commitee.  But I do believe that those five people could create a very fair solution for a full vote topic group.<br>
<br>
Again Dexn we WANT to ensure that anything we enact that SERIOUSLY affects players on the server 24hrs a day 7 days a week should have widespread support.  Think about any of the mobs presently scheduled.  I think all of them could easily get 2/3 of a majority to schedule them (fire giants excluded).  Remember the vast majority of things we vote on will restrict and control how people spend their time.  I don't wanna force that on the server if it is a 51/50 vote.<br>
